{"tid":2032741,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【秘密警察】梁振英：倘發生危害全國安全情況，香港警隊無能力處理","createTime":"2020-05-24T08:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T18:04:06.000Z","uid":7542,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8a92919e7aff2ce168fc15f23eadad681b594e70","tid":2032741,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:26:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528039-20200524.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528039-20200524.htm&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtVKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=951a5c46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528039-20200524.htm&h=a277c5f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528039-20200524.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n全國人大審議決定草案，授權人大常委會就「港區國安法」立法及執行機制事宜。全國政協副主席梁振英認為，如果特區政府的執法部門，有能力應付香港的情況，可授權特區的部門執法，甚麼時候由特區部門處理則要視乎形勢。不過，他說若有人「迫出」一種危害國安的情況，要令中央必須出手的話，相信中央亦會出手。<br />\n<br />\n至於屆時是否由香港警方執法，正在北京出席兩會的梁振英，接受本台訪問時說，要視乎常委會定出的法律條文。他說香港有些危害國安的行為，受影響的是香港，有些則影響國家其他地方，因此要有代表國家的機構設於香港，對影響全國的情況，香港警隊無能力處理。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英說，警隊在港英政府管治時設有龐大的政治部，但英國撤出管治前就被解散，過去20多年警隊沒有類似部門執行維護國安的任務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F-SKS89xxRg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF-SKS89xxRg&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtVKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=31d45269\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F-SKS89xxRg</a>"},{"pid":"0dd64c0fa2123ab58fd45be86a95d68bb65917f6","tid":2032741,"uid":36952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a92919e7aff2ce168fc15f23eadad681b594e70","tid":2032741,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:26:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528039-20200524.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528039-20200524.htm&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtVKtFW5C59xXAv